'''Canada''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, Ottawa, along with Calgary, Edmonton, Halifax, Montreal, Quebec City, Regina, Saskatoon, Toronto, Vancouver, and Winnipeg.

On iOS, Canada provides free healthcare, making characters able to consult doctors and treat [[Diseases|diseases and ailments]] free of charge.

Two [[Achievements]] are Canada-based; ''"There's Always Canada,"'' where a non-Canadian citizen emigrates to Canada, and ''"Winnipeg, EH?"'' where a character vacations (by themselves in [[Activities]] or during childhood when parents offer to take them on vacation) to Winnipeg, Canada.

Along with the [[United States]], Canada allows characters in [[Education|University]] to rush a sorority or fraternity.
